# Server Architecture Guide

## Overview

* **Layers** - standardized levels of abstraction
* **Slices** - feature-based divisions within layers
* **Segments** - technical purpose divisions within slices

```
┌─────────────┬────────────┬────────────┐
│   Layers    │   Slices   │  Segments  │
├─────────────┼────────────┼────────────┤
│   routes    │      -     │      +     │
│   modules   │      +     │      +     │
│   widget    │      +     │      +     │
│   features  │      +     │      +     │
│   entities  │      +     │      +     │
│   shared    │      -     │      +     │
└─────────────┴────────────┴────────────┘
```


